subject: Automobile Racing
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Brendan Gaughan took the lead after a green-white-checkered restart and held on to win the rain-soaked Nascar Nationwide Series race in Elkhart Lake, Wis.
